    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create financial incentives for employers who retain contractors",
        "additional_details": "This should support numerous people left without work in automotive and other industries, and should also therefore help the UK economy",
        "background": "Sectors such as the automotive industry use a large number of contractors alongside permanent staff. Due to IR35 and the COVID pandemic lots of contractors were suspended. The Government should offer financial incentives to companies that wereusing contractors if they agree to call contractors back.",
